{"tid":2305022,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"突發！大貓退出美國市場","createTime":"2020-11-29T09:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T07:52:49.000Z","uid":32511,"like":211,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"9d8b58f4faf5fb9d44254faac64e36fd29322db6","tid":2305022,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T09:47:17.000Z","msg":"金融時報（FT）報導，知情人士透露，滙豐集團（HSBC）在評估如何改善北美事業欠佳的<br />\n績效後，已經縮減選項，現正考慮徹底退出美國消費者金融市場。<br />\n <br />\n報導引述消息人士說，高階主管打算數周內向董事會呈報這項計畫，以利滙豐把資源從美<br />\n國撤出、轉往更賺錢的亞洲事業部門。<br />\n <br />\n若果真結束美國消金事業，這將象徵滙豐40年來致力在美國經營全方位服務、綜合銀行（<br />\nuniversal bank）的時代落幕。美國消金部門今年1至3季的稅前虧損達5.18億美元，去年<br />\n和前年已分別虧損2.79億美元和1.82億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/x0MXE1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2Fx0MXE1&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiZUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=8946db8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/x0MXE1</a>"},{"pid":"8f7a1fa67e430d46150c7bb47adc28b52a6e02b5","tid":2305022,"uid":16057,"like":93,"dislike":5,"score":88,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T09:48:52.000Z","msg":"收到風過多一兩個月就比人制裁想先發制人？"},{"pid":"40891b70da6da9340778b0540c7cd439d23b39ac","tid":2305022,"uid":53922,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T09:49:46.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"green\"> ~~升JOY~~</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></p>"},{"pid":"35d96b31215f98c416d586eda73883fd58115eb9","tid":2305022,"uid":53959,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T09:50:41.000Z","msg":"直接執柒左佢啦"},{"pid":"b45c5459b62d23886bd96c5ce5185f8807831766","tid":2305022,"uid":7250,"like":126,"dislike":4,"score":122,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T09:51:40.000Z","msg":"佢有冇諗過佢中國賺到錢都係因為美國有業務"},{"pid":"6145611af508bb897286